    <div class="wrap">
      <h1>Services</h1>
      <p class="sub">Commercial loan underwriting support, independent portfolio reviews, risk rating validation, and special projects — delivered like your own credit department.</p>

      <div class="grid grid-2">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Loan Underwriting Support</h3>
          <p><strong>What we do:</strong></p>
          <ul>
            <li>C&I, CRE, construction, equipment, and working capital lines</li>
            <li>Financial spreading, ratio analysis, and industry benchmarking</li>
            <li>Complete credit memos formatted to your templates</li>
          </ul>
          <p><strong>Typical deliverables:</strong></p>
          <ul>
            <li>Credit memo (Word/PDF)</li>
            <li>Ratio analysis with commentary</li>
            <li>UCA/global cash flow (as applicable)</li>
            <li>Risk rating recommendation with rationale</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>Portfolio Reviews & Risk Rating Validation</h3>
          <p><strong>What we do:</strong></p>
          <ul>
            <li>Independent validation of assigned risk ratings</li>
            <li>Concentration and stress testing analysis</li>
            <li>Narrative support for rating changes</li>
          </ul>
          <p><strong>Typical deliverables:</strong></p>
          <ul>
            <li>Risk rating worksheet (numeric grid + narrative)</li>
            <li>Portfolio summary with key metrics</li>
            <li>Recommendations for rating or policy updates</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>Special Projects</h3>
          <p><strong>What we do:</strong></p>
          <ul>
            <li>M&amp;A credit due diligence</li>
            <li>Loan policy review and gap analysis</li>
            <li>Compliance preparation and exam readiness checks</li>
          </ul>
          <p><strong>Typical deliverables:</strong></p>
          <ul>
            <li>Project-specific analysis and reporting</li>
            <li>Executive summary for board/committee</li>
            <li>Supporting schedules and exhibits</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>Temporary Capacity Support</h3>
          <p><strong>What we do:</strong></p>
          <ul>
            <li>On-demand credit analysis during peak volume or staff leave</li>
            <li>Operate as an integrated extension of your credit team</li>
          </ul>
          <p><strong>Why it matters:</strong> Avoid backlogs, maintain service levels, and keep deals moving without adding headcount.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

